reviews.review_text:
MeBeHappy!!! Nice show for me ...

Nice work with the audio clean-up ... 

What else can set my bonehead attitude right for the day except to listen to some of that stufff...

Maybe a bong-load or three ...
Nice clean show Really nice recording, very mellow and has some great renditions of some favorites :).

I want to tell you how it's gonna be.. ready for something else besides 5/8/77
---This would be a real good choice!

Prefer Keith on the Piano myself. 
But he is up in the mix here.
Stellar Wow. Loser. Bertha. FOTM. GDTRFB. Franklin’s Tower. All great...and the Loser is in my top 25 of all versions. They were on. Wish I was there
